     /// # Fallback Order
     ///
     /// 1. **Vault secrets** (primary source): `secret/data/codetether/providers/<provider_id>`
     /// 2. **Bedrock auto-detection** (if not in Vault): Reads `AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID`, `AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY`
